p-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\">API地址：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/product/tclm\" target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.tencent.com/product/tclm</a></span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\">Github ：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;background-color: transparent;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan</a></span></span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\">HuggingFace：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;background-color: transparent;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/tencent\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/tencent</a></span></span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\">C3-Bench：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/C3-Benchmark\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/C3-Benchmark</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\">ArtifactsBench：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/ArtifactsBenchmark\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/ArtifactsBenchmark</a></span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯混元开源首个 13B 激活参数的 MoE 模型 Hunyuan-A13B，性能优异且推理速度快，在 Agent 工具调用和长文能力表现突出",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯混元开源首个 13B 激活参数的 MoE 模型 Hunyuan-A13B，性能优异且推理速度快，在 Agent 工具调用和长文能力表现突出",
  "summary": "腾讯混元发布了首个开源的混合推理 MoE 模型 Hunyuan-A13B，总参数 80B，激活参数仅 13B，性能比肩同等架构领先开源模型，推理速度更快且性价比更高。该模型在多个权威测试集上表现优异，尤其在 Agent 工具调用和长文能力上突出，支持 256K 原生上下文窗口。Hunyuan-A13B 采用快慢思考模式优化计算资源分配，对个人开发者友好，仅需 1 张中低端 GPU 卡即可部署。腾讯还开源了两个新数据集 ArtifactsBench 和 C3-Bench，以填补行业评估标准空白。该模型已在腾讯内部 400+业务中使用，日均请求超 1.3 亿。腾讯混元将持续推进多尺寸、多场景的全系模型开源，促进大模型开源生态繁荣。",
